xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 31, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yzp1709198831196.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yzp1709198831196.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yzp1709198831196.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yzp1709198831196\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> widget is a listbox control that contains a list of\n\t\tpossible values. You can select one or more values in a <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> widget. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_pyy_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e55\">Default Logical Widgets</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The default logical widget is <code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Select</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_knr_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e67\">Triggers</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">(web)trigger onchange: This trigger is fired when the value is changed. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_qsx_clm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e76\">Extends fluent-select Web Component</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This widget is implemented using the Fluent web component fluent-select. Most of its features\n\t\t\t\tare also available in this widget. Most of its events are mapped to triggers. For\n\t\t\t\tmore information, see the Fluent documentation on the fluent-select web\n\t\t\t\tcomponent.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_ic2_dg2_q1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e85\">Keyboard support</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__ul_spf_1dl_q1c\">\n<li class=\"li\">Vertical scrolling keys to navigate listbox</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Pressing the Enter key opens listbox</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Pressing the Enter key from listbox selects item and closes listbox</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_inh_lqh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e106\">Layout processing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Widget class method <code class=\"ph codeph\">processLayout()</code> constructs the template HTML for this\n\t\t\t\twidget. It generates nodes for the control itself as well as slots for label and\n\t\t\t\terror icon, and returns it to Uniface. Use this function to enhance the widget with\n\t\t\t\tmore static features.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_hf4_frh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e119\">Widget properties</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> widget supports the following properties:<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Property</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:readonly</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the widget as being read-only.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:hidden</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a boolean value that hides or shows a select.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:disabled</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the widget as being disabled.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">class:classname</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Boolean value that adds or removes a specified class.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">display-format</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines how values are displayed by the widget. The available\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\toptions are:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__ul_qs2_tjn_tcc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">rep</code>: Displays the representation only.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThis is a default value.</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">val</code>: Displays the value only.</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">valrep</code>: Displays both value and\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trepresentation.</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">show-placeholder</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines whether to display a placeholder or not.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">placeholder-text</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a placeholder text in case the value is null and property\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">show-placeholder</code> is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<kbd class=\"ph userinput\">true</kbd>. The default text value is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">Select item</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">label-position</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the position of the label with respect to its widget. The available options\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tare:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__ul_dkx_bw1_kbc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">above</code>(default)</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">below</code></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">before</code></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">after</code></li>\n</ul><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__note_ayk_2wh_kbc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If the label-position is not\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdefined for the widget, then it is aligned by default above\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe widget.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">popup-position</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the position for the popup to open in a specified\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdirection. The available options are:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__ul_dcv_jth_qcc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Above</code></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Below</code>. This is a default value.</li>\n</ul><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__note_xjd_4th_qcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The popup's behavior depends on\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe viewport. For example - If a user defines\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">popup-position=above</code>, and if there is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tno space above for a select popup to open, it will open\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbelow, regardless of the defined position. This behavior is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thandled by Fluent. </div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">exclude</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"yzp1709198831196__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines that there will be no column for the field in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code>.<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__note_uhf_fnn_tcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tis actually not a widget property. It is a field property,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tused by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code> widget if that is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe containing entity's widget.</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_yvb_hdn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e333\">Helper and validation error visualization</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">A <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> widget deals with the following error visualizations:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__ul_jqz_cfl_q1c\">\n<li class=\"li\">Red color border alert</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Alert icon (after suffix icon) </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Tool-tip when hovering the \"Alert icon\" showing the error message</li>\n<li class=\"li\">When the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> has focus, no red border is shown, only error icon is\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshown</li>\n<li class=\"li\">When the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> does not have a focus, both red border and error icon is\n\t\t\t\t\t\tshown</li>\n<li class=\"li\">A <samp class=\"ph systemoutput sysout\">no-representation-error</samp> error is shown if the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfield value does not have a corresponding representation. This includes a\n\t\t\t\t\t\tnull value if the property is not set.</li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_vnb_ndn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e375\">UI blocking</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When the field is in transaction, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxselect</code> widget blocks user\n\t\t\t\tinput by becoming read-only.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__section_c4l_z4m_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1098749e387\">Widget styling</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" id=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" name=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\">CSS Selector</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" id=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" name=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\">Selected node(s)</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">27 rows found</div></div><div><button aria-label=\"Export table to a file\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageTableExportButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-v\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-v\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicPageTableExportMenu\"><button aria-label=\"Export to Excel\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to Excel</button><button aria-label=\"Export to CSV\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to CSV</button></div></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scroll\" data-testid=\"sticky-header-table\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHead\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHeadInner\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; width: 709px; padding-right: 0px;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; width: 709px;\"><caption></caption><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\"><th aria-controls=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c\" aria-label=\"CSS Selector: activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 299.656px;\" tabindex=\"0\"><strong class=\"ph b\">CSS Selector</strong></th><th aria-controls=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c\" aria-label=\"Selected node(s): activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" id=\"yzp1709198831196__table_xsc_ljl_q1c__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 358.344px;\" tabindex=\"0\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Selected node(s)</strong></th></tr>\n<tr class=\"searchTableDiv\"><td><label aria-hidden=\"fal